OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774569807
OL,3,CBrits warned of delays ahead of Easter
OL,4,C- what is the EU's new entry system?
OL,6,FBritish holidaymakers are being warned
OL,7,Fto be aware of extra border checks
OL,8,Fwith the new EU Entry Exit System
OL,9,Fahead of the Easter Holidays.
OL,11,FThe Entry Exit System is supposed to
OL,12,Fmake entering the EU from a non-
OL,13,FSchengen area country quicker, and is
OL,14,Fphasing out physical stamps from
OL,15,Fpassport officers, in place of a
OL,16,Fdigital biometric system.
OL,18,FIt has been introduced to strengthen
OL,19,Fborder security, detect overstays and
OL,20,Fis supposed to improve processing
OL,21,Fspeeds at airports.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
