FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774569807
OL,3,CBrits warned of delays ahead of Easter
OL,4,C- what is the EU's new entry system?
OL,6,FFrom Friday, 10 April, EES is set to
OL,7,Fbe fully implemented at all EU
OL,8,Fairports and ports, with passport
OL,9,Fstamps no longer needed.
OL,11,FBut until then, many airports are
OL,12,Feffectively running a double system,
OL,13,Fwith both passport stamps being taken
OL,14,Fand the new biometric digital EES also
OL,15,Fbeing carried out.
OL,17,FThis double-entry recording has led to
OL,18,Fnumerous delays at airports across the
OL,19,Fbloc, with Brits complaining of multi-
OL,20,Fhour waits to get through airports.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774569807
OL,3,CBrits warned of delays ahead of Easter
OL,4,C- what is the EU's new entry system?
OL,6,FThe problem has been particularly bad
OL,7,Fduring busy periods, and with the
OL,8,FEaster weekend coming up just before
OL,9,Fthe 10 April deadline, the British
OL,10,Fgovernment has urged people to check
OL,11,Fthey have all of the right
OL,12,Fdocumentation needed for seamless
OL,13,Fentry under the EES and be prepared
OL,14,Ffor delays.
OL,16,FWhat is the Entry Exit System?
OL,18,FNon-EU nationals wishing to enter the
OL,19,FSchengen area will now go through
OL,20,Fbiometric checks instead of getting a
OL,21,Fpassport stamp when entering the area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774569807
OL,3,CBrits warned of delays ahead of Easter
OL,4,C- what is the EU's new entry system?
OL,6,FThese checks will involve face scans
OL,7,Fand fingerprint recording. Children
OL,8,Funder the age of 12 will not need to
OL,9,Fhave their fingerprints scanned.
OL,11,FTravellers will also go through the
OL,12,Fsame check when leaving the area,
OL,13,Fmeaning country's can track when
OL,14,Fvisitors overstay.
OL,16,FOnce registered, subsequent entries to
OL,17,Fthe bloc will be quicker, as the
OL,18,Fbiometrics will only need to be
OL,19,Fscanned rather than registered. The
OL,20,Fdigital record will be valid for three
OL,21,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774569807
OL,3,CBrits warned of delays ahead of Easter
OL,4,C- what is the EU's new entry system?
OL,6,FTravellers will not need to take any
OL,7,Faction before their journey.
OL,9,FWho will be affected?
OL,11,FThe changes will mostly affect people
OL,12,Ffrom non-EU countries, including those
OL,13,Ffrom the UK.
OL,15,FIt affects all countries in the
OL,16,FSchengen area, which includes France,
OL,17,FSpain and Germany. Ireland is not
OL,18,Fwithin this area and travel there is
OL,19,Fnot be impacted by the new rules.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
