PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774569807
OL,3,CBrits warned of delays ahead of Easter
OL,4,C- what is the EU's new entry system?
OL,6,FFor travellers using the Eurostar at
OL,7,FSt Pancras, Eurotunnel LeShuttle at
OL,8,FFolkestone, or the Port of Dover, EES
OL,9,Fregistration takes place before
OL,10,Fleaving the UK. Otherwise,
OL,11,Fregistration happens on arrival in the
OL,12,Fdestination country.
OL,14,FCruise ship journeys starting and
OL,15,Fending at UK ports are exempt from the
OL,16,FEES rules unless passengers disembark
OL,17,Fto continue their holiday within the
OL,18,FSchengen area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
