FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774569807
OL,3,CBrits warned of delays ahead of Easter
OL,4,C- what is the EU's new entry system?
OL,6,FIt should only take a few minutes, but
OL,7,Fthere have been reports of significant
OL,8,Fdelays as airports struggle with the
OL,9,Fnew system.
OL,11,FThere is a small list of other
OL,12,Fexceptions for UK nationals, which can
OL,13,Fbe found on the EES website.
OL,15,FWhy has the EU introduced the new
OL,16,Fsystem?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
