OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774569807
OL,3,CBrits warned of delays ahead of Easter
OL,4,C- what is the EU's new entry system?
OL,6,FFull list of countries using the EES
OL,7,Fsystem:
OL,9,FAustria, Belgium, Bulgaria, Croatia,
OL,10,FCzech Republic, Denmark, Estonia,
OL,11,FFinland, France, Germany, Greece,
OL,12,FHungary, Iceland, Italy, Latvia,
OL,13,FLiechtenstein, Lithuania, Luxembourg,
OL,14,FMalta, Netherlands, Norway, Poland,
OL,15,FPortugal, Romania, Slovakia, Slovenia,
OL,16,FSpain, Sweden, and Switzerland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
